    Bloodlust.Description = "<font size='19'>Apply Bloodlust to yourself, granting +[1]% damage for each character in a [2] radius around you. Pay up to X more AP: X is equal to the number of other characters within range: For each AP you cannot pay in this way, apply 2 Battered and Harried to yourself.</font><br><br><font color='46b195'>Source Infusions:</font><font size='17'><br><font color='46b195'>1: </font>You are left with at least 1AP after casting. Emulate the effects of Whirlwind within 5m.<br><font color='46b195'>2 (requires 5 Warfare): </font>When you hit an enemy while performing a basic attack, apply up to Weakened III for 2 turns. Gain the Executioner talent for 2 turns. Recover 1SP.<br><font color='46b195'>3 (requires 9 Warfare): </font>Once per round, per target, your basic attacks also perform a Battle Stomp on the target struck and recover 2AP.<br><font color='858580' size='18' face='Averia Serif'><br>Tiered statuses apply up to tier 3 and reduce resistances; see your journal for a full description.</font></font>"

